title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: A diplomatic gesture in the name of friendship creates a win-win scenario for you and an ally. Otherwise, you might balk at someones losing proposition or unfair ultimatum. No one wants to feel forced or guilt-tripped into an agreement. Think outside of the box to envision other possibilities. Once you are free from past limitations, you can ask your friend to entertain a different idea. However, its important that you stand your ground on your non-negotiables. There are no winners if you lose yourself to this interpersonal tug-of-war and ignore your needs in the process. Old ways wont open new doors. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
